# {{ dist }}

{{ description }}

Built on the [FLEXT](https://github.com/flext-sh/flext) typed platform: canonical
facades (`c`/`m`/`p`/`t`/`u`/`r`), `r[T]` result contracts on every fallible path,
and Pydantic v2 settings/config (ADR-005).

## Install

```bash
uv pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Layout

```
src/{{ package_name }}/
  api.py          # public facade ({{ class_stem }} / {{ alias }})
  base.py         # service base (s[TResult])
  constants.py    # c.{{ ns }}.*
  models.py       # m.{{ ns }}.*
  protocols.py    # p.{{ ns }}.*
  typings.py      # t.{{ ns }}.*
  utilities.py    # u.{{ ns }}.*
  _settings.py    # settings.{{ class_stem }} (env-override, prefix {{ env_prefix }})
  _config.py      # config.{{ class_stem }} (config/*.yaml, ADR-005)
  config/{{ ns_attr }}.yaml
  services/       # domain services composed into the facade
tests/            # flext_tests shim + smoke tests
```
